OL,5, An Italian trial into the 2018 Genoa   
OL,6, bridge disaster that killed 43 people  
OL,7, has heard it was known for years there 
OL,8, was a risk it might collapse.          
OL,10,F"I didn't do anything and it's my      
OL,11,Fgreatest regret," said Gianni Mion, a  
OL,12,Fformer highways company boss in charge 
OL,13,Fof the bridge and its maintenance.     
OL,15,FDozens of vehicles plunged 45m (150ft) 
OL,16,Fwhen the Morandi bridge collapsed in   
OL,17,Fheavy rain in August 2018.             
OL,19,FMr Mion said the risk was raised at a  
OL,20,Fmeeting eight years before the tragedy.
